text: Punta Gorda may be: *Punta Gorda, Belize *Punta Gorda, Florida *Punta Gorda Light, Humboldt County, California, USA *Punta Gorda, Montevideo, in Uruguay. * Punta Gorda, Nicaragua, the place where Hurricane Felix made landfall as a category 5 hurricane in 2007. *The Punta Gorda coastal area in Ventura County, California ==Related pages== * Puntagorda, a municipality on the Canary island La Palma.
title: Punta Gorda
